  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a heartwarming adventure with Sushi Bot! Decorate your restaurant with game-changing furniture, serve customers quickly to earn a top rating, and complete quests to learn more about your neighbors and discover the mysterious spirits that watch over Rolling Hills.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >  <strong>DECORATE AND DELIVER</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1235100/extras/80ade0a375ec654edaa92ea3db4e786a.poster.avif?t=1774032991\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1235100/extras/80ade0a375ec654edaa92ea3db4e786a.webm?t=1774032991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1235100/extras/80ade0a375ec654edaa92ea3db4e786a.mp4?t=1774032991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Customize your restaurant with furniture that grant practical bonuses and express your style, then serve customers quickly to earn coins and complete quests.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>LEARN FROM YOUR FRIENDS</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1235100/extras/66f35037cc1ece6fd56b10207cb4542f.poster.avif?t=1774032991\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1235100/extras/66f35037cc1ece6fd56b10207cb4542f.webm?t=1774032991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1235100/extras/66f35037cc1ece6fd56b10207cb4542f.mp4?t=1774032991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build relationships and complete quests to gain new upgrades and abilities, like a helpful mini-robot or the power to stop time.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A SPIRITED ADVENTURE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1235100/extras/af7fa858cfd2008d1d4b5a152ae869c9.poster.avif?t=1774032991\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1235100/extras/af7fa858cfd2008d1d4b5a152ae869c9.webm?t=1774032991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1235100/extras/af7fa858cfd2008d1d4b5a152ae869c9.mp4?t=1774032991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you meet the spirits that guard Rolling Hills, you'll lift the town out of obscurity and gain access to otherworldly challenges with unique rewards, like an underwater restaurant!</p>",
