h\" >Build relationships and complete quests to gain new upgrades and abilities, like a helpful mini-robot or the power to stop time.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A SPIRITED ADVENTURE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1235100/extras/af7fa858cfd2008d1d4b5a152ae869c9.poster.avif?t=1774032991\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1235100/extras/af7fa858cfd2008d1d4b5a152ae869c9.webm?t=1774032991\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1235100/extras/af7fa858cfd2008d1d4b5a152ae869c9.mp4?t=1774032991\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you meet the spirits that guard Rolling Hills, you'll lift the town out of obscurity and gain access to otherworldly challenges with unique rewards, like an underwater restaurant!</p>",
